  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN DISCORD</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522010/extras/542ca408594582d0ab7433728d395d08.avif?t=1666890906\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br>If you want to Join follow this Link: </p><br><h1>OVERVIEW</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522010/extras/563152b27f656f9873703237d45dbdfd.avif?t=1666890906\" width=616 height=2088 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Firescout is an Online Multiplayer Shooter Game.<br>Many Gamemodes to Play:<br><br>- Team Deathmatch<br>- Kill Confirmed<br>- Capture the Flag (CTF)<br>- Conquest<br>- Rush<br><br>And the best thing is you can also Play Offline with Bots.<br><br><strong>You are the Killer</strong> <br>Make every round a new adventure and show what you can do.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522010/extras/555ff32fb325c0f9292cc503351aef5e.poster.avif?t=1666890906\" width=800 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522010/extras/555ff32fb325c0f9292cc503351aef5e.webm?t=1666890906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522010/extras/555ff32fb325c0f9292cc503351aef5e.mp4?t=1666890906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Online or Offline Fun</strong><br>Play online with players from all over the world.<br>Or if you don't feel like it, you can simply play offline against bots.<br><br><strong>Unique Levels</strong><br>Many Levels to Play.<br>Every Level is an other Experience for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522010/extras/92c38e0303adb4c7912d9cf89d27f8cf.poster.avif?t=1666890906\" width=800 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522010/extras/92c38e0303adb4c7912d9cf89d27f8cf.webm?t=1666890906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1522010/extras/92c38e0303adb4c7912d9cf89d27f8cf.mp4?t=1666890906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Daily Updates</strong><br>The developers try to bring updates online daily.",
